Feb. 9, 1992 D Milton Keynes Brass Band Festival (Championship Section)
Milton Keynes Brass Band Festival (Championship Section) 1 Entertainments Contest Milton Keynes Brass Band Festival milton-keynes-brass-band-festival-championship-sec
Stantonbury Leisure Centre Sports Hall, Milton Keynes Bands played an entertainment programme including March Of The Mogul Emporers. 24 bands competed. Best Instrumentalist: Kevin Robbins, Cornet, Yorkley
1st Prize: £550.00 (Mk Co-Op trophy) 2nd Prize: £300.00 (Legal & General trophy) 3rd Prize: £200.00 (Yardleys trophy) 4th Prize: £100.00 5th Prize: £50. 20 bands competed.
